flowchart TD
    Start([PDF Upload]) --> Validate{Valid PDF?}
    Validate -->|No| Reject[Reject with reason]
    Validate -->|Yes| Extract[Paper Reader: extract text + segment sections]
    Extract --> ScanSecurity[Security: injection scan + PII mask on extracted text]
    ScanSecurity --> Explain[Research Explainer: 4-level summaries]
    ScanSecurity --> FactCheck[Fact Checker: claim extraction + verification]
    FactCheck --> Related[Related Work: arXiv + Semantic Scholar discovery]
    Related --> Gap[Research Gap: weaknesses + novel ideas]
    Explain --> Quiz[Quiz/Teaching: flashcards + MCQs + study guide]
    Gap --> Presentation[Presentation: slides + speaker notes + poster]
    Quiz --> Aggregate[Coordinator: aggregate all outputs]
    Presentation --> Aggregate
    Aggregate --> Memory[Memory Agent: store summary + insights]
    Memory --> Report([Final report + human-review notice])
